{"tid":1824480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華府指倘英國政府使用華為建設5G是瘋狂決定","createTime":"2020-01-14T13:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T17:26:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c398f5d251c54fece27f1446e1185493e1e40fb5","tid":1824480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"華府指倘英國政府使用華為建設5G是瘋狂決定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502699-20200114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502699-20200114.htm&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=b83b874c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502699-20200114.htm&h=ae993699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502699-20200114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府據報今個月內，決定在日後建造5G網絡「非核心」部分時，是否使用中國電訊設備生產商華為的產品。<br />\n<br />\n美國副國家安全顧問博明率團前往倫敦，與約翰遜政府負責保安政策的國務大臣盧柏敦會面，提出更多有關華為保安風險的證據，形容英方若果仍然使用華為產品「無異於瘋狂的決定」。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相府發言人重申，政府有嚴格監管現時華為如何在英國鋪設設備，並會全面檢視，確保英國日後的5G網絡符合安全，在決定是否讓華為參與後，會通知國會。盧柏敦表示，對於是否採用華為設備，政府「很快就有決定」。"},{"pid":"5b116be5dbd76e35904bf2e78a0a25ad7428b509","tid":1824480,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"[狂開行動] 1.19天下制裁大遊行 - 幫手上熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824479</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},{"pid":"8dd78d5deec40d7f3d39b518b3c9bd5f8304ab12","tid":1824480,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"平<br />\n好撚平"},{"pid":"71cc48477532d4bdef039bfc3700e08b76d6d26a","tid":1824480,"uid":40908,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"英國想引狼入室<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7493acc356065f23bf47452b126dbccac8ff56ad","tid":1824480,"uid":58054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"梗係貪佢平啦<br />\n唔通貪佢好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d3e37c86a48cdd6f07e9e5bdf52880e2514aad","tid":1824480,"uid":268537,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"因為窮,華為平到好唔合理<br />\n就算明知有後門都要買"},{"pid":"252ed63a31b5c3184450124b60e18b9ab6837672","tid":1824480,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"cia<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f716abad804aaf3734e5c978bdb4c8d7c1b6992","tid":1824480,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"日落帝國"},{"pid":"95f57104a83434685597d163273459595e3e9a8c","tid":1824480,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"華為直接用支那政府資助去你國家起基礎建設<br />\n一定係可以低價過商業社會嘅其它公司<br />\n呢個係佢所謂嘅&quot;優勢&quot;<br />\n5G唔係好撚高不可攀嘅科技 <br />\n短波頻高速傳輸技術你起得夠多基站服務質素就愈好<br />\n而歐洲地方大需求基站數量更多<br />\n華為每件平nokia/ericsson 少少圍返出嚟條數已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講即係平時慣用技量<br />\n華為係支那用嚟利用國家資源打擊外國公司嘅矛<br />\n咁當然除咗成本低啲<br />\n有某啲國家嘅政府更加係想維持同中國長技貿易先會引華為入屋<br />\n出賣國家安全換錢"},{"pid":"f3d018eefeb22708a7cb17ac711aba136bae1891","tid":1824480,"uid":104645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"廢國最後奶共都唔意外"},{"pid":"8cab0590ec8af6617406d53d851d2104e212c5c9","tid":1824480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"英國首相莊漢生：華為批評者必須提出替代方案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56401b61eb62435d0839327e285837f5d79cf7b","tid":1824480,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得未來有一日英國會廢左英軍， 用解放軍代替防衛， 軍事成本又可以慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b946b2dac83a8288fee5d7bf36e65c2690463d","tid":1824480,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔一直幻想嘅大英帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfb527d8ddbc4acb023a9fd5d342b61c2256828","tid":1824480,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cff3306b53022f03102fc80feb8b70fe2b2e8075","tid":1824480,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實諗唔撚明點解一定要用華為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"華為用左咁多年都無安全問題<br />\n但係美國監聽就有發生過德國總理的確係比美國監聽過<br />\n<br />\n平根本係好次要既問題 政府點會比唔起錢<br />\n同埋真係好用 有咩問題國家級既解決速度 保證穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛立信承認行賄都唔夠華為黎 因為真係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3aa0c9a2a067eeaac221fcc5cd5cbc5eaf51e5","tid":1824480,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"快啲用啦 好想睇戲"}]}